Parliament, Tuesday, 12 February 2019 – The Select Committee on Appropriations will tomorrow engage the Eastern Cape Department of Social Development on its progress with implementing the Early Childhood Development Grant. Details of the meeting are as follows: Date: Wednesday, 13 February 2019 Time: 10:00 
	Venue: Cape Town Lodge Hotel, 101 Buitengracht St
	Cape Town City Centre ISSUED BY PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE ACTING CHAIRPERSON OF THE SELECT COMMITTEE ON APPROPRIATIONS, MR CHAREL DE BEER. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Felicia Lombard (Ms)
